title: theaoo Egg Holder for Fridge, Automatic Rolling Egg Container for Refrigerator, Clear Plastic Egg Dispenser, Stackable Eggs Organizer with Quick Removable inner Tray For Organizers and Storage, 2Pack
features: The automatic ball bearing design ensures that each egg moves smoothly without tearing or getting dirty. Allows quick access to eggs.
Compact storage holds 12 to 14 eggs or more when you stack two eggs
The quick removable inner shell makes it easy to fill a new egg.

Stackable drawer design, different from other egg holders. If you store other items in our egg holder, you don't need to pull out the entire egg holder after the eggs are used up. Simply remove the inner compartment to quickly load new eggs. Reduce products when other items are moved back and forth.
The transparent top allows you to clearly see if you have no eggs, and is easy to clean. Hand wash only. Not suitable for dishwasher. Patented Product: D1007542
Unlike other products, the lid does not need to be completely removed. Simply pull out the inner tray to easily fill the eggs.
